Leaf and calyx micromorphological data revealed straight flexuose (villose), subappressed, hairs and small glandular trichomes having a 1-2 celled stalk and single head, on both surfaces of the leaves (
Fig. 3A
) and adaxial surface of the outer and inner sepals (
Fig. 3B
).

